              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Panggilan</span></p><p>Tahap Selesai: Mengakibatkan 1 <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/19/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_783450697057953645.png",
                "id": "talent95294",
                "key": "Shadowsword: Lone Gale",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/19/25750596/01ccafbe27188aef259b0286fd0b4545_2973771054573965954.png",
                "title": "Shadowsword: Lone Gale"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p>Tahap Selesai: Mengakibatkan 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/19/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6248657376764403656.png",
                "id": "talent3948",
                "key": "Shadowsword: Galloping Frost",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/19/25750596/e7a414623d5d709d441b0ca6779155bf_3461976110487414309.png",
                "title": "Shadowsword: Galloping Frost"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Cryo DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Hydro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Electro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/19/25750596/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_7906501815521742554.png",
                "id": "talent79293",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Cryo dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/19/25750596/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_7280600803108461719.png",
                "id": "talent82243",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_5924673297046872157.png",
